                                </span>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col col-12 col-md-4 col-xl-3 p-2">
                                <div class="input-group">
                                    <span class="input-group-text">Servs</span>
                                    <select data-bind="value: Servings, valueUpdate: 'afterkeydown'"
                                        class="form-select">
                                        <option value="">Choose</option>
